                            <comment id="16460963" author="njiang" created="Wed, 2 May 2018 12:39:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=dentych&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;dentych&quot;&gt;dentych&lt;/a&gt; How can you access the route? I&apos;m trying to reproduce the error.&lt;br/&gt;
It could be great if you can past the curl command to access the camel route.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16460980" author="dentych" created="Wed, 2 May 2018 12:54:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=njiang&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;njiang&quot;&gt;njiang&lt;/a&gt; I have added the cURL command I used to the description. Sorry about that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16461141" author="njiang" created="Wed, 2 May 2018 15:04:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue is caused by the camel cannot find a right type convert from InputStream to ByteBuffer.&lt;br/&gt;
You can workaround this issue by adding the convertTo(byte[].class) just like this &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;rest&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;/pi&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
            .get()
            .route()
            .setExchangePattern(ExchangePattern.InOut)
            .to(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;https4:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//api.pi.delivery/v1/pi?bridgeEndpoint=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).convertBodyTo(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;byte&lt;/span&gt;[].class);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; </comment>
                            <comment id="16461862" author="njiang" created="Thu, 3 May 2018 02:41:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=dentych&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;dentych&quot;&gt;dentych&lt;/a&gt; You can also add a &lt;a href=&quot;http://camel.apache.org/type-converter.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;type converter&lt;/a&gt; from the InputStream to ByteBuffer to fix the NPE without changing the route. I will commit a quick fix for this issue shortly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16461877" author="njiang" created="Thu, 3 May 2018 03:22:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Applied the patch into master, camel-2.21.x and camel-2.20.x branches.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
